title: 10 Min HIIT Cycle Bike Workout
description:
10 Min HIIT Cycle Bike Workout

Trying to squeeze a workout into your busy day? This quick 10-minute cycle bike HIIT is a great way to make the most of your time. Follow along with Sunny Trainer Sydney as you push your body to the limit all in just 10 minutes. 

Warm-up 
1 min Progressive 

Workout 
12x 30 sec on (high resistance, all out cadence); 15 sec off (easy recovery)

END WORKOUT
